023import static org.apiguardian.api.API.Status.STABLE;
024
025import javax.lang.model.element.Modifier;
026import java.lang.reflect.Type;
027import java.util.Set;
028
029import org.apiguardian.api.API;
030import org.tquadrat.foundation.annotation.ClassVersion;
031import org.tquadrat.foundation.javacomposer.internal.FieldSpecImpl;

033/**
034 *  The specification for a generated field declaration.
035 *
036 *  @author Square,Inc.
037 *  @modified   Thomas Thrien - thomas.thrien@tquadrat.org
038 *  @version $Id: FieldSpec.java 857 2021-01-23 00:00:26Z tquadrat $
039 *  @since 0.0.5
040 *
041 *  @UMLGraph.link
042 */
043@ClassVersion( sourceVersion = "$Id: FieldSpec.java 857 2021-01-23 00:00:26Z tquadrat $" )
044@API( status = STABLE, since = "0.0.5" )
045public sealed interface FieldSpec
046    permits FieldSpecImpl
047{
048        /*---------------*\
049    ====** Inner Classes **====================================================
050        \*---------------*/
051    /**
052     *  The specification of a builder for an instance of an implementation for
053     *  {@link FieldSpec}
054     *
055     *  @author Square,Inc.
056     *  @modified   Thomas Thrien - thomas.thrien@tquadrat.org
057     *  @version $Id: FieldSpec.java 857 2021-01-23 00:00:26Z tquadrat $
058     *  @since 0.0.5
059     *
060     *  @UMLGraph.link
061     */
062    @SuppressWarnings( "InnerClassOfInterface" )
063    @ClassVersion( sourceVersion = "$Id: FieldSpec.java 857 2021-01-23 00:00:26Z tquadrat $" )
064    @API( status = STABLE, since = "0.0.5" )
065    public static sealed interface Builder
066        permits FieldSpecImpl.BuilderImpl
067    {
068            /*---------*\
069        ====** Methods **======================================================
070            \*---------*/
071        /**
072         *  Adds an annotation for the field.
073         *
074         *  @param  annotationSpec  The annotation.
075         *  @return This {@code Builder} instance.
076         */
077        public Builder addAnnotation( final AnnotationSpec annotationSpec );
078
079        /**
080         *  Adds an annotation for the field.
081         *
082         *  @param  annotation  The annotation.
083         *  @return This {@code Builder} instance.
084         */
085        public Builder addAnnotation( final Class<?> annotation );
086
087        /**
088         *  Adds an annotation for the field.
089         *
090         *  @param  annotation  The annotation.
091         *  @return This {@code Builder} instance.
092         */
093        public Builder addAnnotation( final ClassName annotation );
094
095        /**
096         *  Adds annotations for the field.
097         *
098         *  @param  annotationSpecs The annotations.
099         *  @return This {@code Builder} instance.
100         */
101        public Builder addAnnotations( final Iterable<AnnotationSpec> annotationSpecs );
102
103        /**
104         *  Adds a Javadoc comment for the field.
105         *
106         *  @param  block   The comment block.
107         *  @return This {@code Builder} instance.
108         */
109        public Builder addJavadoc( final CodeBlock block );
110
111        /**
112         *  Adds a Javadoc comment for the field.
113         *
114         *  @param  format  The format.
115         *  @param  args    The arguments.
116         *  @return This {@code Builder} instance.
117         */
118        public Builder addJavadoc( final String format, final Object... args );
119
120        /**
121         *  Adds modifiers for the field.
122         *
123         *  @param  modifiers   The modifiers.
124         *  @return This {@code Builder} instance.
125         */
126        public Builder addModifiers( final Modifier... modifiers );
127
128        /**
129         *  Builds a new
130         *  {@link FieldSpec}
131         *  instance from the added components.
132         *
133         *  @return The {@code FieldSpec} instance.
134         */
135        public FieldSpec build();
136
137        /**
138         *  Sets the initializer for the field.
139         *
140         *  @param  codeBlock   The code that initialises the field.
141         *  @return This {@code Builder} instance.
142         */
143        public Builder initializer( final CodeBlock codeBlock );
144
145        /**
146         *  Sets the initializer for the field.
147         *
148         *  @param  format  The format.
149         *  @param  args    The arguments.
150         *  @return This {@code Builder} instance.
151         */
152        public Builder initializer( final String format, final Object... args );
153    }
154    //  interface Builder
155
156        /*---------*\
157    ====** Methods **==========================================================
158        \*---------*/
159    /**
160     *  Creates a builder for an instance of {@code FieldSpec} from the given
161     *  type, name and modifiers.
162     *
163     *  @param  type    The type of the {@code FieldSpec} to build.
164     *  @param  name    The name for the new field.
165     *  @param  modifiers   The modifiers.
166     *  @return The new builder.
167     *
168     *  @deprecated Replaced by
169     *      {@link JavaComposer#fieldBuilder(Type, CharSequence, Modifier...)}.
170     */
171    @SuppressWarnings( "removal" )
172    @Deprecated( since = "0.2.0", forRemoval = true )
173    @API( status = DEPRECATED, since = "0.0.5" )
174    public static Builder builder( final Type type, final CharSequence name, final Modifier... modifiers )
175    {
176        final var retValue = FieldSpecImpl.builder( type, name, modifiers );
177
178        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
179        return retValue;
180    }   //  builder()
181
182    /**
183     *  Creates a builder for an instance of {@code FieldSpec} from the given
184     *  type, name and modifiers.
185     *
186     *  @param  type    The type of the {@code FieldSpec} to build.
187     *  @param  name    The name for the new field.
188     *  @param  modifiers   The modifiers.
189     *  @return The new builder.
190     *
191     *  @deprecated Replaced by
192     *      {@link JavaComposer#fieldBuilder(TypeName, CharSequence, Modifier...)}.
193     */
194    @SuppressWarnings( "removal" )
195    @Deprecated( since = "0.2.0", forRemoval = true )
196    @API( status = DEPRECATED, since = "0.0.5" )
197    public static Builder builder( final TypeName type, final CharSequence name, final Modifier... modifiers )
198    {
199        final var retValue = FieldSpecImpl.builder( type, name, modifiers );
200
201        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
202        return retValue;
203    }   //  builder()
204
205    /**
206     *  Creates a builder for an instance of {@code FieldSpec} from the given
207     *  type, name and modifiers.
208     *
209     *  @param  type    The type of the {@code FieldSpec} to build.
210     *  @param  name    The name for the new field.
211     *  @param  modifiers   The modifiers.
212     *  @return The new builder.
213     *
214     *  @deprecated Replaced by
215     *      {@link JavaComposer#fieldBuilder(TypeSpec, CharSequence, Modifier...)}.
216     */
217    @SuppressWarnings( "removal" )
218    @Deprecated( since = "0.2.0", forRemoval = true )
219    @API( status = DEPRECATED, since = "0.0.5" )
220    public static Builder builder( final TypeSpec type, final CharSequence name, final Modifier... modifiers )
221    {
222        final var retValue = FieldSpecImpl.builder( type, name, modifiers );
223
224        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
225        return retValue;
226    }   //  builder()
227
228    /**
229     *  {@inheritDoc}
230     */
231    @Override
232    public boolean equals( final Object o );
233
234    /**
235     *  {@inheritDoc}
236     */
237    @Override
238    public int hashCode();
239
240    /**
241     *  Checks whether the given modifier was applied to this field.
242     *
243     *  @param  modifier    The modifier.
244     *  @return {@code true} if the given modifier has been applied to this
245     *      field.
246     */
247    public boolean hasModifier( final Modifier modifier );
248
249    /**
250     *  Returns the modifiers for this field.
251     *
252     *  @return The modifiers.
253     */
254    public Set<Modifier> modifiers();
255
256
257    /**
258     *  Returns the name for this field.
259     *
260     *  @return The name.
261     */
262    public String name();
263
264    /**
265     *  Returns a builder that is already initialised with the components that
266     *  built this field.
267     *
268     *  @return The builder.
269     */
270    public Builder toBuilder();
271
272    /**
273     *  {@inheritDoc}
274     */
275    @Override
276    public String toString();
277
278    /**
279     *  Returns the type of the field.
280     *
281     *  @return The type.
282     */
283    public TypeName type();
284}
285//  interface FieldSpec
